This is [Richard Lehane](https://richardlehane.me)’s personal website. 

I’m an archivist and consultant in digital recordkeeping and digital preservation. I do a little programming, including:

- [siegfried](/siegfried), a file format identification tool,
- [Siplicity](https://sipli.city), a digital preservation triage tool,
- and [Authority Editor](https://authorityeditor.com), an editor for drafting retention schedules in XML.

